des:
BNETA IoT products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off BNETA IoT bulbs or plugs.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your BNETA IoT products - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Replace your App name products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “BNETA IoT” app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one account in our “BNETA IoT” app;
(3). You need to have some BNETA IoT devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "BNETA IoT" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "BNETA IoT" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "BNETA IoT" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "BNETA IoT", and you'll be navigated to App name login page;
(9). Input your BNETA IoT account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
“Alexa, Turn on plug”.
“Alexa, Turn off plug”.
